<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="on-the-occasion-of">on the occasion of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>在…之际：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I traveled back to my hometown <strong>on the</strong> sad <strong>occasion of</strong> Dad’s death.
在父亲去世的悲痛时刻我回到了家乡。</p><footer>2012浙江</footer></div></div>